### Create invite (super admin — tenant in path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/9/invites
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "email": "michael.scott@example.com",
  "roleId": 51,
  "specialistId": 8
}

### Create invite (tenant admin — path must match JWT tenantId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/9/invites
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "email": "jane.scott@example.com",
  "roleId": 50
}

### Create invite with specialist (links profile on register when invite has specialistId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/9/invites
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "email": "specialist.user@example.com",
  "roleId": 50,
  "specialistId": 1
}

### Delete invite (tenant admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenants/8/invites/53
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
